    "2) Dataset and Task Categories: Evaluation conducted using 28,715 human instructions annotated with:• Task specifications and safety constraints.• Environmental metadata (dynamic obstacles, temperature sensitivity).",
    "Three primary task categories:• Navigation: \"Navigate to dining area avoiding obstacles.\"",
    "• Manipulation: \"Handle fragile cup placement on tray.\"",
    "• Multi-Step: \"Fetch coffee and serve at table 5.\"",
    "Evaluation MetricsQuantitative assessment using five key metrics:• Ambiguity Resolution Rate (ARR): Successfully clarified instructions Total ambiguous instructions × 100."
